
Name: Pedernales River Chili 
Description: LBJ's chili recipe

Ingredients

4lb chili meat
1 large onion, chopped
2 cloves garlic
1t ground oregano
1t comino seed
6t chili powder
1.5C canned whole tomtoes
2-6 generous dashes liquid hot sauce
2C hot water
salt

Instructions

Place meat, onion and garlic in large, heavy pan or dutch oven
Cook until light in color
Add oregano, comino seed, chili powder, tomatoes, hot pepper sauce, salt and hot wter
Bring to a boil, lower heat, and simmer for about 1 hour.
Skim off fat during cooking